00:37:03.726 --> 00:37:08.576 A:middle
This kid was in -- you know,
he was using, you know,

00:37:08.576 --> 00:37:09.806 A:middle
single words to communicate.

00:37:10.156 --> 00:37:15.736 A:middle
And you can see that he's not
